<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="run-n">run <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /rʌn/    美 /rʌn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 跑；跑步：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>go for</strong> a <strong>run</strong> 
去跑步</p><footer>外研⑦ – 2</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>After every run I feel fitter and happier. 
每次跑完步，我都感到更健康、更快乐。</p><footer>2011 湖南改</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[常用单数] 态势；趋势：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the run of the market 
市场走势</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-over-the-long-run">in / over the long run</h3>
<p>1.<strong>从长远看：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A true friend will advise us to do what he thinks is best for us in the long run. 
真正的朋友会建议我们做从长远来看对我们有利的事。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>runner /'rʌnə(r)/ n [C]  </p></div>